==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Self-motion
<hw>Self`-mo"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Motion given by
inherent power, without external impulse; spontaneous or voluntary
motion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Matter is not induced with <qex>self-motion</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Cheyne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-moved</ent>⟦br⟧
